stimulusitem1: Each machine can give you any of the 4 types of stamps. However, the red machines are more likely to give you stamps that let you gain MANY points (tools, +10 points) but also stamps where you lose MANY points (faces, -9 points).    On the other hand, the blue machines are more likely to give you stamps where you gain LESS points (animals, +2 points) but also stamps where you lose LESS points (places, -1 points).  To remind you of this while playing, you will see numbers above each machine. The numbers in BOLD tell you the amount of points that machine is more likely to give you...             Press Spacebar to continue
